{"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem"]}],"kind":"symbol","schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"symbolKind":"struct","roleHeading":"Structure","role":"symbol","modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"title":"OUDSSwitchItem","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSSwitchItemV","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"struct"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}]},"topicSections":[{"title":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/init(_:isOn:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:isReadOnly:hasDivider:)"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers"},{"title":"Instance Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body"],"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties"},{"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations","generated":true}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"]}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"Layouts","level":2,"text":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"inverse","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}]}]}]},{"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Indicator states"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Particular cases"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"An ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the ","type":"text"},{"code":"isError","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" flag is risen.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","text":"Accessibility considerations","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom switch trait."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","text":"Forbidden by design","type":"heading"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}]},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}]}],"type":"paragraph"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Code-samples","level":2,"text":"Code samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, helper: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additonal label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\",","                   helper: \"1967\",","                   isReversed: true,","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                   isReversed: true,","                   isError: true,","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Design-documentation","level":2,"text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/18acc0-switch"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Themes-rendering","level":2,"text":"Themes rendering"},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange","level":3,"text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Orange","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","level":3,"text":"Orange Business Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_OrangeBusinessTools"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Orange-Inverse","level":3,"text":"Orange Inverse"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_OrangeInverse","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Sosh","level":3,"text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"type":"heading","anchor":"Wireframe","text":"Wireframe","level":3},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Wireframe","type":"image"}]},{"type":"aside","name":"Version","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"1.1.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"style":"note"},{"type":"aside","name":"Since","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.14.0","type":"text"}]}],"style":"note"}]}],"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some swith components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a switch with only an indicator, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitch","type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"sections":[],"references":{"component_switchItem_OrangeBusinessTools":{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Orange